          "name": "Conditions",
          "type": "[]metav1.Condition",
          "json_tag": "conditions,omitempty",
          "doc": "Conditions is a list of status conditions that provide information about the observed state of the InferencePool. This field is required to be set by the controller that manages the InferencePool. Supported condition types are: * \"Accepted\" * \"ResolvedRefs\" +listType=map +listMapKey=type",
